N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14ยง 9.1 - Part 100 of title 22 of official compilation of codes, rules and regulations adopted and incorporated by reference

State Regulations

The provisions of the rules governing procedure under article
730 of the Criminal Procedure Law adopted by the Judicial Conference and
appearing as Part 100 of Title 22 (Judiciary) of the Official Compilation of

Codes, Rules and Regulations of the State of New York are hereby adopted and
incorporated in Appendix 12 of this Title. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes
R. & Regs. Tit. 14ยง
9.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
